want to believe in the eldritch manifestations he brings into light. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eMy favorites in this collection: \"Dagon,\" \"The Festival,\" \"The Call of Cthulhu,\" \"The Colour Out of Space,\" and \"The Whisperer in Darkness.\"\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\"I choose weird stories because they suit my inclination best—one of my strongest and most persistent wishes being to achieve, momentarily, the illusion of some strange suspension or violation of the galling limitations of time, space, and natural law which forever imprison us and frustrate our curiosity about the infinite cosmic spaces beyond the radius of our sight and analysis.\"\u003cbr /\u003e-H. P. Lovecraft","rating":4,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/13015682?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3005056587"},"likeCount":40,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":3,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Work:kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.6n8EiFxh8DOaYtgGDqi4mA":{"id":"kca://work/amzn1.gr.work.v1.6n8EiFxh8DOaYtgGDqi4mA","__typename":"Work","legacyId":6750943,"bestBook":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.28BjbxtrTS5wljeQ8bx9hA"},"details":{"__typename":"WorkDetails","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/6750943-the-call-of-cthulhu-and-other-weird-stories","shelvesUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/work/shelves/6750943-the-call-of-cthulhu-and-other-weird-stories","publicationTime":-1388505600000,"originalTitle":"The Call of Cthulhu and Other Weird Stories","awardsWon":[],"places":[],"characters":[{"__typename":"Character","name":"Inspector John Raymond Legrasse","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/characters/38283-inspector-john-raymond-legrasse"},{"__typename":"Character","name":"Cthulhu","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/characters/95293-cthulhu"}]},"reviews":{"__typename":"BookReviewsConnection","totalCount":1761,"edges":[{"__t